Gesture Inspector

Portions of this project are derived from the MediaPipe Gesture Recognizer
Android sample at https://github.com/google-ai-edge/mediapipe-samples and retain
copyright notices for The TensorFlow Authors. The exact upstream sample revision
was not recorded in this repository and should be established before external
redistribution.

Project-specific modifications and additional code are provided under the
Apache License, Version 2.0. MediaPipe Android libraries declare Apache-2.0 in
their published metadata. The build replaces MediaPipe Tasks'
`TasksStatsLoggerFactory` with a small factory for MediaPipe's bundled
`TasksStatsDummyLogger`; the surrounding MediaPipe classes retain their
upstream license and notices.

The build downloads the gesture recognizer model bundle from:
https://storage.googleapis.com/mediapipe-models/gesture_recognizer/gesture_recognizer/float16/1/gesture_recognizer.task
SHA-256: 97952348cf6a6a4915c2ea1496b4b37ebabc50cbbf80571435643c455f2b0482
Model card:
https://storage.googleapis.com/mediapipe-assets/gesture_recognizer/model_card_hand_gesture_classification_with_faireness_2022.pdf

The model is not stored in Git, but it is packaged into built APKs. The download
endpoint and model card do not state complete redistribution terms; confirm the
applicable upstream model license before distributing an APK.
